Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm Griffith. What's your name?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guts.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where am I?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.81,0:00:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Band of the Hawk.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will get my own kingdom...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:00:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guts... I'll be the one to decide{\i}\N{\i1}the place where you'll die.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.46,0:01:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't there anyone who can stop{\i}\N{\i1}those black devils of Chuder?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He is my...my...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When his ambition dies within him...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.04,0:01:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}death will come to you!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.71,0:01:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A death you cannot escape!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.88,0:01:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Behelit.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She said it's the destiny of one{\i}\N{\i1}who holds it to acquire the world...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.82,0:01:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in exchange for his flesh and blood.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill who?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will you do it?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just give me an order{\i}\N{\i1}like you always do.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To simply live a life{\i}\N{\i1}because one was born into it...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't accept that.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A friend is someone who{\i}\N{\i1}does not cling to another's dream.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:01:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He decides his own dream.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:02:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and he will stand against anyone...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who dares to trample on it{\i}\N{\i1}with his body and soul.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if that person is me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A friend to me. is an equal.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.14,0:04:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To simply live a life{\i}\N{\i1}because one was born into it...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't accept that...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Band of the Hawk is\Nmost impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they are single-handedly shutting down\Nthe enemy's right flank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith... He was a good find.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If only Count Julius were alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Our army is like a bird\Nwith only one wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The Band of the Hawk will make\Nthemselves even more indispensable...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:04:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at a time like this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman who commands\Na thousand of the Band of the Hawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman playing at being a knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you got\Nyour rank of commander
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,by crawling into Griffith's bed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The battlefield is\Nthe sacred ground of men!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare a woman set foot upon it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Adon, head of the Blue Whale\NUltra Heavy Armored
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Fierce Assault Annihilation\NKnight Corps
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,shall teach you the folly\Nof your actions!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Casca!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiots! Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Spineless fools who allow themselves\Nto be led by a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't even put up a fight... Not surprising\Nsince you let a woman order you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NIs that all you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a joke that they call you\Nthe commander of a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Band of the Hawk really scraped\Nthe bottom of the barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not so bad-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll overlook your earlier insolence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say?\NCome to Chuder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall have a thousand...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you\Na thousand Chuder soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can keep them warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone will do. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like swinging this\Nas hard as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So you countered, eh kid.\NNot bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was just a lucky break!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My ultimate spear technique\Nhas been passed down
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,through the Coborlwitz family\Nfor over 140 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Take my ultimate secret technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ganzansenpu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ganzansenpu...\NWhat the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:07:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not alert...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Casca!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Snap out of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Cas...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Big Sis!\N- Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Casca!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never swimming\Nin this get up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She's burning up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't stay in this rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta find somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts and Casca?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,From that height,\Nwho knows what happened to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of which,\NGuts was wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to dispatch\Na search party now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Count Griffith, we are at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I adamantly oppose weakening\Nour formation for two mere soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the highly touted Captain\Nof the Raiders
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the female commander\Nof a thousand, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, they can find\Ntheir way back on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am in total agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll take off whatever's soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She kept on fighting\Neven though she had a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why women are so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The idiot... She's hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be rough being a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you have something to protect.{\i}\N{\i1}take up that sword.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A cave by the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily, falling into\Nthe river saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...river?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Lie down, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fever hasn't dropped yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.10,0:14:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You were soaking wet\Nand freezing to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you-!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you-!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you... Cut it out, you bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I risked my life to pull you\Nout of the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you weren't a woman,\NI'd punch you and knock your jaw out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A "woman"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, flipping out like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why women\Ndon't belong on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask...to be born a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pitiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one\NI didn't want to be saved by!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still not well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You really hate me, don't you...\Ndamn it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What Griffith said to you that day,\Non the hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want you. Guts.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith has never said\Nthat to anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not before, and not since.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did it have to be you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,his sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you sure they're around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure they're not dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They fell off that cliff, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Adon said he'd pay\Nthe bounty even for their corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look a little further downstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk. You need to\Nsave your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I found you brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You're looking lively, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Impudence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not just going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll administer the torture technique\Npassed down through the Coborlwitz family
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,for two hundred years...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The hundred-year convulsive death...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...and show you what hell\Non earth is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the woman here for\Nthe mercenary soldiers to feast on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She's pretty vicious.\NShe'll bite it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Such insolence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a run for it straight\Ninto the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!\NI'm not going to run off alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The sick will only get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Archers! Aim for the woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sacrificing himself not once,\Nbut twice for a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A sword returns to its sheath.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home to your sword master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Griffith.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think about an answer\Nto your question earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:19:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not fear!\NThere are only two of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Surround them and attack at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll return with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let the woman get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go chase after girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,after you finish your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,His left hand is useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't be able swing that\Nridiculously big sword anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is getting interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure caused us\Na lot of trouble, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you-!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I so...weak?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even think about\Nbiting your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to be alive for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.47,0:22:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go back to your sword master.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.31,0:22:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't bite my tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you have your way\Nwith me either!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.66,0:22:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you-!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.57,0:23:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Casca?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.98,0:23:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts stayed back with the enemy...\Nso I could escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.22,0:23:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Send every man available!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.43,0:23:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the hell am I doing...?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.07,0:23:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a stupid place like this...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.27,0:23:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}risking my life...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so cheaply?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A dream he must realize for himself.{\i}\N{\i1}and himself alone.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.23,0:23:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To simply live a life{\i}\N{\i1}because one was born into it...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.93,0:24:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't accept that.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A friend to me...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.54,0:24:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is...an equal.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.10,0:24:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You call yourselves men of Chuder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.68,0:24:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no time to think...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.75,0:24:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now. all there is...{\i}\N{\i1}is how to cut...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.68,0:24:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}how to kill...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.39,0:24:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all there is.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.51,0:25:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope we make it in time!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.15,0:25:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.39,0:25:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.90,0:25:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the Captain do all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.40,0:25:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. There must be\Nclose to a hundred...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.97,0:25:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.94,0:25:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me, Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.55,0:26:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.02,0:26:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.66,0:26:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.90,0:26:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.20,0:26:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't look good...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.17,0:26:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.57,0:26:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.54,0:26:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you breaking\Nyour promise to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.55,0:26:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts...!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.32,0:26:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.72,0:26:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shake me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.16,0:26:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes my wounds hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.90,0:26:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.54,0:26:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.91,0:26:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, the Captain's a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.64,0:26:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys probably didn't think\Nthat they could lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.05,0:27:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.85,0:27:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Band of the Hawk has\Nthe "Guts" to slay a hundred men!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.76,0:27:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Guts who slew\Na hundred men!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.09,0:27:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hurrah!\N- Hurrah!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.17,0:27:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.61,0:28:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.21,0:28:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a single man can get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.71,0:28:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder Doldrey is so feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.66,0:28:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Holy Purple Rhino Knights!\NBoscogn is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.71,0:28:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Their defense is impregnable and\Nany enemy is easily repelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.68,0:28:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the exhausted forces\Ncome under assault
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.58,0:28:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,by the Holy Purple Rhino Knights,\Nreputedly Chuder's strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.15,0:28:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result of this audacious tactic,\Nthe loss to our army,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.65,0:28:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,including our elite White Tiger Knights,\Nhas climbed to 30%.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.89,0:28:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Any more losses...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.03,0:28:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that already!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.80,0:28:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Doldrey was long\Na stronghold of Midland.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.10,0:29:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it cannot\Nbe penetrated easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.17,0:29:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There is internal conflict in Chuder\Nover the next succession to the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.54,0:29:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They do not have the reserves\Nto focus on a battle here...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.31,0:29:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If this becomes\Na long, drawn-out battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.05,0:29:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.71,0:29:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Doldrey is Chuder's last foothold.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.52,0:29:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We must defeat Chuder and\Nend this Hundred Years' War now...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.12,0:29:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.42,0:29:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He is right.\NThis is our one-in-a-thousand chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.16,0:29:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.07,0:29:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Chuder is suffering as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.87,0:29:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My generals, how do you feel\Nabout total warfare?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.81,0:29:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I am opposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.77,0:29:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Morale is low and\Nmen are deserting like flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.94,0:29:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,With the White Tiger Knights annihilated...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.05,0:29:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, we still have remnant enemy\Nforces to deal with in our territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.02,0:29:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If the enemy should attack\Nfrom the rear,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.96,0:29:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the situation will be irreparable.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.83,0:30:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If this military expedition continues,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.16,0:30:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there will be need for\Nadditional defense funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.36,0:30:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,More taxation will burden\Nthe citizens...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.90,0:30:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- and lead to unrest...\N- Even you must consider this situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.70,0:30:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,a dilemma, Sir Hawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.04,0:30:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were so ordered...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.37,0:30:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.77,0:30:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even for a genius of warfare\Nsuch as yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.68,0:30:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.42,0:30:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If His Majesty so ordered me...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.59,0:30:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need for a large force.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.69,0:30:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Band of the Hawk\Nwill take this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.40,0:30:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- What did you-?!\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.66,0:30:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.43,0:30:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Band of the Hawk to\Nrecapture Doldrey by themselves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.07,0:30:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the White Tiger Knights\Nwere annihilated...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.97,0:30:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in your right mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.57,0:30:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We are talking about\Na mere 5,000 on horseback
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.51,0:30:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,against an army 30,000 strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.84,0:30:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous! This is the foolish talk\Nof a novice!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.08,0:30:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Over these one hundred years,\Ncountless distinguished generals
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.78,0:30:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,have attempted and failed\Nto conquer Doldrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.05,0:31:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Band of the Hawk cannot manage\Nsuch a feat alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.06,0:31:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Griffith, was that sincere?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.54,0:31:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I command the Band of the Hawk\Nto capture Doldrey!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.02,0:31:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Band of the Hawk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.29,0:31:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Roughly 5,000 of them\Nare headed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.19,0:31:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They expect to take Doldrey\Nwith a mere 5,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.16,0:31:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they...?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.46,0:31:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,General Boscogn...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.70,0:31:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.93,0:31:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith the White Hawk must\Nnot be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.57,0:31:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.67,0:31:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring the Hawk here alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.88,0:31:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.28,0:32:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.41,0:32:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as he is alive,\Nthe Band of the Hawk...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.75,0:32:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather, the momentum of\NMidland cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.65,0:32:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,General Boscogn!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.79,0:32:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.82,0:32:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.74,0:32:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it... How are we supposed\Nto attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.71,0:32:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The back of it is a cliff...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.41,0:32:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got 20 of\Nthe latest catapults.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.62,0:32:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.52,0:32:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be rained upon with arrows,\Nhot oil and rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.72,0:32:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice\Nbut to attack from the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.22,0:32:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's the Holy Purple\NRhino Knights too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.53,0:32:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We can win, can't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.23,0:32:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.53,0:32:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.10,0:32:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The fortress is a little big, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.61,0:33:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do what Griffith says\Nand it will be ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.61,0:33:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.99,0:33:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.76,0:33:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Setting up formation with\Nthe river behind them?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.53,0:33:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't they know anything\Nabout military strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.73,0:33:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is,\Nconsidering the size of their force,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.00,0:33:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just a desperate tactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.34,0:33:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We will take them straight on,\Nnothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.71,0:33:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.25,0:33:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.98,0:33:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.65,0:33:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,General Adon,\NI'm glad to see you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.06,0:34:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything happen in my absence?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.67,0:34:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.65,0:34:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanguard...onward!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.89,0:34:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Draw your swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.30,0:34:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanguard, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.08,0:34:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is on the move!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.35,0:34:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Count Griffith himself leads\Nthe vanguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.25,0:34:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest number roughly 2000.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.42,0:34:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's divided his already\Nsmall army into two?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.82,0:34:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,With the General himself\Nat the fore?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.29,0:34:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting, let us take him on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.99,0:35:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Call up the advance guard!\NDestroy the enemy's first wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.24,0:35:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.91,0:35:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! We can't stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.61,0:35:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Holy Purple Rhino Knights\Nare being pushed back!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.58,0:35:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.55,0:35:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,G-General!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.05,0:35:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.89,0:35:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.72,0:36:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He's taking advantage of\Nthe mobility of a light cavalry
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.76,0:36:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to force through our line.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.53,0:36:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Put our heavy cavalry directly\Nbefore the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.66,0:36:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And archers, commence attack\Nfrom both flanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.60,0:36:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do now, Hawk?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.81,0:36:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.05,0:36:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to make us scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.32,0:36:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Boscogn! What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.39,0:36:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith could very well be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.71,0:36:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanguard! Fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.54,0:36:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Return to the main force!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.61,0:36:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Go straight through them!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.78,0:37:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.02,0:37:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.72,0:37:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is retreating.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.09,0:37:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.63,0:37:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He should have anticipated\Nthis result from the very start.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.43,0:37:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Band of the Hawk\Nwho knows only victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.63,0:37:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Hawk, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.30,0:37:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing,\NGeneral Boscogn...?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.71,0:37:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Governor General!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.41,0:37:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is retreating.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.98,0:37:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you let victory slip out\Nof our hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.88,0:37:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No...well...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.18,0:37:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.85,0:37:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A reward of your asking\Nawaits anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.26,0:37:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,who captures the enemy general,\Nthe White Hawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.72,0:37:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he must be taken unharmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.46,0:37:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.70,0:37:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Governor General! It is unwise to\Nmake such a lofty promise to soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.10,0:37:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They will be uncontroll-
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.40,0:37:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,General Boscogn...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.30,0:37:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your service
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.14,0:38:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Gennon, will be taking command.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.94,0:38:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Holy Purple Rhino Knights\Nwill henceforth
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.91,0:38:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,join the Blue Whale, Black Wolf,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.81,0:38:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and my Scorpion Serpent Assault\NKnights in pursuing the enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.32,0:38:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and to swiftly capture Griffith.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.55,0:38:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about defending the fortress?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.79,0:38:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.66,0:38:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you not hear my order,\NGeneral Boscogn?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.27,0:38:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,General...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.57,0:38:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.67,0:38:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,However, kill the Hawks without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.71,0:38:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot allow them to\Nhave free rein any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.04,0:38:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.31,0:38:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We will begin pursuit of the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.48,0:39:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we supposed to...\Ntake on all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.37,0:39:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Take formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.21,0:39:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The river is behind us.\NWe have no escape route!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.54,0:39:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Lay down your lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.21,0:39:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other chance\Nfor survival!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.51,0:39:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do survive,\Nwe will stand victorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.68,0:40:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.36,0:41:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy force is small.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.03,0:41:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mow them down
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.06,0:41:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,before they have a chance to\Npull any cheap tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.64,0:41:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.95,0:41:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather die fighting than\Ndrown in some river!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.28,0:41:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Rickert's lost it!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.07,0:41:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.34,0:41:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts, the Captain of the Raiders,\Nfrom the Band of the Hawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.44,0:41:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see a thing.\NWhat's going on out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.04,0:41:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even bother worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.84,0:42:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The outcome is obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.35,0:42:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more interested in when\Nwe'll get some booze around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.42,0:42:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who snares the enemy general\Nwill get any reward he asks for...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.12,0:42:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and I get stuck with this stupid duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.46,0:42:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.90,0:42:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.73,0:42:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a different enemy force!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.35,0:42:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, something's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.56,0:42:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Adon, we have intruders\Nin the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.33,0:42:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.13,0:42:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Hurry and close the gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.27,0:42:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not allow messengers to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.50,0:43:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Barbier and Benoit troops\Nwill do as planned
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.24,0:43:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and subdue all remaining\Nenemy troops!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.77,0:43:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Every second counts!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.54,0:43:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith was right about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.61,0:43:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to hand it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.62,0:43:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.99,0:43:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a foolish woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.12,0:43:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making a big mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.26,0:43:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,if you think things\Nwill go your way so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.19,0:43:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you no mercy this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.39,0:43:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Casca!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.40,0:43:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.07,0:43:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll deal with him myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.50,0:43:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.38,0:43:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.69,0:43:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's strong...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.66,0:43:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What is taking Boscogn so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.33,0:44:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let up. Push them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.34,0:44:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.79,0:44:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.52,0:44:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fighting like\Na different person!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.03,0:44:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I'm physically sound,\NI'd never lose to a bastard like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.50,0:44:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis really is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.74,0:44:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got this under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.17,0:44:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry with the preparations!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.91,0:44:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right!\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.82,0:44:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.94,0:45:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Boscogn...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.88,0:45:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the fighting spirit\Nyou had earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.05,0:45:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, your arm is dropping!\NIs your sword too heavy for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.79,0:45:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even muster a retort.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.30,0:45:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's the Captain of the Raiders!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.93,0:45:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.81,0:45:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.01,0:45:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Coborlwitz Family Distraction\NTechnique, honed over 1000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.35,0:45:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell right for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.52,0:45:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Big Sis!\N- Commander Casca!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.72,0:45:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.85,0:46:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Such pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.62,0:46:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you'll still be proud
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.59,0:46:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,when I amuse myself with you\Nbefore your men.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.06,0:46:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get a good taste\Nof your soft skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.63,0:46:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall teach you what true joy\Nis to a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.90,0:46:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.74,0:46:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a good taste of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.05,0:46:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Commander Casca!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.29,0:46:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You had us mesmerized!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.79,0:46:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost precious time. Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.57,0:46:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.84,0:46:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll assist!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.58,0:47:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This side first!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.15,0:47:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.12,0:47:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's too much for you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.85,0:47:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nuisances!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.37,0:47:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over, Captain of the Raiders!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.04,0:48:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- General Boscogn was...!\N- No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.08,0:48:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The strongest knight in Chuder!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.14,0:48:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, he did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.88,0:48:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boscogn!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.78,0:48:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not panic.\NHe is completely outnumbered!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.72,0:48:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get into formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.74,0:48:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What is...that banner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.21,0:48:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!\NThe fortress couldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.11,0:48:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.75,0:48:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiots, haven't you figured it out yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.79,0:48:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your general is dead.\NYour fortress has fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.52,0:48:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious what that spells?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.76,0:48:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.56,0:48:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Cry out!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.20,0:48:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Cry out for victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.30,0:49:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.42,0:49:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Show no mercy if\Nthe enemy offers opposition!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.70,0:49:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools! Who ordered you to retreat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.44,0:49:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your Supreme Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.84,0:49:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.04,0:49:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow my orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.28,0:49:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Come back! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.67,0:50:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time,\NLord Gennon.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.31,0:50:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.45,0:50:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith! How I have waited\Nfor this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.52,0:50:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Come...let me have\Na closer look at your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.72,0:50:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Those eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.96,0:50:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That gaze has not changed\Nsince that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.96,0:50:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NWhy are you so quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.47,0:50:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We may have parted foes,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.17,0:50:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but I never forgot about you\Nfor a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.91,0:50:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I always looked for your shadow...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.04,0:50:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Griffi...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.28,0:50:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.15,0:50:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you look at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.25,0:51:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you resent me?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.69,0:51:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not resent you, Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.69,0:51:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, just the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.86,0:51:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,By using you, I was able to provide\Nfor hundreds of my subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.77,0:51:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Without having to send them\Nonto a treacherous battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.14,0:51:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We all owe you our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.01,0:51:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.05,0:51:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only do one thing for\Nmy subordinates who share my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.28,0:51:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That is to continue winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.85,0:51:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I do not choose the method.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.32,0:51:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You were like a stone lying\Nby the side of the path I walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.70,0:51:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.52,0:53:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Three cheers for\Nthe Band of the Hawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.12,0:53:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The savior of Midland!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.99,0:53:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!\NWe are grateful for your efforts!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.83,0:53:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.29,0:53:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.96,0:53:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Lord Griffith!\N- How handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.86,0:54:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you look at this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.43,0:54:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know so many people\Nlived in Windham.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.57,0:54:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.81,0:54:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No fair, Corkus!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.01,0:54:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,One at a time. One at a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.42,0:54:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.05,0:54:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Casca! Look this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.26,0:54:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's the Raiders!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.49,0:54:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I see Captain Guts too!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.76,0:54:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the strongest warrior\Nin the Hawks!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.87,0:54:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.71,0:54:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it, Captain?\NWave to the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.58,0:54:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the hero of this battle,\Nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.88,0:54:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.02,0:54:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.95,0:54:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NYou've been in a daze.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.02,0:54:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've been so quiet, lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.46,0:55:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.56,0:55:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody would've thought of\Nsomething like this three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.40,0:55:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.77,0:55:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will get my own kingdom...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.85,0:55:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody but him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.63,0:55:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.44,0:55:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.44,0:55:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.31,0:55:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they from the Band of the Hawk?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.31,0:55:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the guardians of Midland!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.68,0:55:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to look sharp,\Nor they'll make fun of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.42,0:56:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Lord Griffith.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.85,0:56:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We were very worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.79,0:56:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I prayed for you every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.43,0:56:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a dance partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.13,0:56:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to hear the exploits of\Nthe Band of the Hawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.53,0:56:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you get bored listening\Nto barbaric tales of battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.40,0:56:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.11,0:56:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They're very stimulating.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.94,0:56:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a natural!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.98,0:56:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.64,0:56:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He could at least send one our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.71,0:56:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the captains of\Nthe Band of the Hawk, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.45,0:56:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.28,0:56:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to hear\Nyour heroic tales of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.19,0:56:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.56,0:56:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.76,0:56:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, do regale us.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.13,0:56:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I couldn't finish in a single night...\NDo you have the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.73,0:56:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All the time in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.40,0:56:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Captain of the Raiders?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.83,0:56:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He slew one hundred of\Nthe enemy by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.40,0:56:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.77,0:56:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one who brought down\NGeneral Boscogn too.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.61,0:57:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my... Who's stronger?\NYou or Lord Griffith?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.48,0:57:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Amazing muscles!\N- Oh, so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.22,0:57:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I could fall in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.12,0:57:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.25,0:57:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you belong to\Nthe Band of the Hawk too?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.86,0:57:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.02,0:57:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, who should attack but...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.79,0:57:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The knights led by General Boscogn!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.13,0:57:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- Give me a break...\N- None other than...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.63,0:57:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey! No fair, Guts!\N- The Holy Purple Rhino...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.84,0:57:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.98,0:57:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.68,0:57:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone else already ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.15,0:57:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.98,0:57:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No man could possibly ignore\Na woman like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.29,0:57:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How about after him then?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.09,0:57:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no... I am after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.82,0:57:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.06,0:57:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I would love to sing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.83,0:57:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.07,0:57:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I hate nobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.64,0:57:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.54,0:58:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guys won't leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.64,0:58:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.44,0:58:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.45,0:58:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so much easier just\Nto swing around a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.36,0:58:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.02,0:58:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't do things\Nwe're not used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.03,0:58:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't worn a skirt in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.60,0:58:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have all these muscles now.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.04,0:58:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I look funny, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.04,0:58:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.51,0:58:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You look pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.18,0:58:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.88,0:58:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.15,0:58:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go and\Nask Griffith for a dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.42,0:58:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd only step on his toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.10,0:59:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So what made you change?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.47,0:59:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You never used to show up\Nat these stuffy functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.91,0:59:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd see it for myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.34,0:59:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.51,0:59:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see just what Griffith and\Nthe Band of the Hawk have accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.85,0:59:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All the things\Nhe's managed to get so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.25,0:59:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything he's going to try\Nto get from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.99,0:59:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts, are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.33,0:59:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.46,0:59:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of being part of his dream\Nand looking up at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.38,0:59:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.08,0:59:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't allow to take me for granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.12,0:59:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...not...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.85,0:59:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Excellency!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.26,1:00:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Excellency!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.51,1:00:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, you have endured well\Nover these many months of tribulation.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.15,1:00:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my sincerest thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.06,1:00:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As you are aware,\Nthis victory was all due
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.56,1:00:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to the work of the Band of the Hawk\Nled by Count Griffith.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.13,1:00:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,For nearly 100 years,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.57,1:00:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the capture of Doldrey had been\Nconsidered an impossible task.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.44,1:00:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But with great daring and courage,\Nthey accomplished it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.78,1:01:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, I am bestowing the name,\Nthe White Phoenix Knights,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.22,1:01:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to Count Griffith and\Nhis Band of the Hawk,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.12,1:01:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the first time such a rank and\Nhonor has been granted.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.93,1:01:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Phoenix General!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.10,1:01:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Phoenix Knights!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.27,1:01:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.18,1:01:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.28,1:01:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, they will...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.11,1:01:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.95,1:01:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not dreaming, after all.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.92,1:01:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're nobles!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.65,1:04:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurrah for the Band of the Hawk...!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.13,1:05:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.52,1:06:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts, we've argued many times,\Nbut we've braved death together.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.36,1:06:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All the hardship the Band of the Hawk\Nendured is finally paying off.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.53,1:06:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is only the beginning.\NWhy would you...?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.44,1:06:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.14,1:06:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.91,1:06:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.22,1:06:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You intend on quitting\Nthe Band of the Hawk?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.42,1:06:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.96,1:06:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.40,1:06:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Band of the Hawk\Nis your family!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.07,1:06:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What reason could you possibly\Nhave to abandon us?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.47,1:06:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We can be nobles!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.94,1:06:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be able to live a life\Nthat's straight out of a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.38,1:06:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What misgivings could you have?!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.58,1:07:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A grown man made the decision,\Nso let's respect it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.25,1:07:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But...!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.02,1:07:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all against it, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.32,1:07:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts is vital to\Nthe Band of the Hawk!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.69,1:07:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Band of the Hawk isn't strong\Njust because of him!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.26,1:07:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.03,1:07:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.84,1:07:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is as good an occasion as any\Nto say this!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.37,1:07:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've hated you from the very start.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.78,1:07:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And I finally figured out\Nwhy you irritate the hell outta me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.05,1:07:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that face of yours!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.82,1:07:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking so smug...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.38,1:07:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,like you're the only one\Nwho's got serious troubles.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.65,1:07:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You really make me sick!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.72,1:07:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's something else!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.46,1:07:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All that we had to endure to\Nget here means nothing to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.20,1:07:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So let him throw it all away\Nlike yesterday's trash.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.67,1:07:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk the path of suffering\Nas much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.94,1:08:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're looking for,\Nbut you'll never be Griffith.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.71,1:08:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.82,1:08:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If we ever meet up on the battlefield,\Nwatch your back!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.86,1:08:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, that felt good!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.57,1:08:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything, guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.04,1:08:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Guts!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.75,1:08:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you that day...\Nthat you belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.26,1:08:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist on leaving...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.69,1:08:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,wrest yourself away\Nby your sword.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.43,1:09:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.63,1:09:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can't just leave with\Na smile and a "take care"?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.87,1:09:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you mean business.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.74,1:09:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.88,1:09:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're comrades!\NAre you really going to fight?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.62,1:09:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith, if you want to stop him,\Ntalk it through!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.92,1:09:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Casca, don't get in our way.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.83,1:09:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pippin, what're you doing? Let go!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.13,1:09:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.73,1:09:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if he gets an arm cut off,\Nhe'll come to his senses.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.64,1:09:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with all of you?\NStop them!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.77,1:09:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the good life in\Na real army make you forget?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.01,1:09:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're taken with a sword,\Nyou take yourself back with a sword.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.81,1:09:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the rule for mercenaries like us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.75,1:09:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.09,1:09:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.73,1:10:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...stand against anyone who dares to{\i}\N{\i1}trample on it with his body and soul.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.87,1:10:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if that person is me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.92,1:10:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you so determined...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.03,1:10:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to leave my grasp?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.17,1:10:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can't...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.21,1:10:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can't!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.31,1:10:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't allow it!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.25,1:11:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.17,1:11:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.16,1:12:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.03,1:12:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.67,1:12:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.54,1:13:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.17,1:13:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A princess of a kingdom going out\Nto meet a gentleman of common birth...?!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.94,1:13:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Griffith now is\Nthe General of the White Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.71,1:13:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the highest rank\Nin the Midland army!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.42,1:13:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That is only after\Nnext month's installation.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.82,1:13:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna, do keep an eye on her.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.19,1:13:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him in six months.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.23,1:13:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,At least...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.98,1:13:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when we finally have peace...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.93,1:13:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.14,1:14:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Griffith...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.25,1:14:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.86,1:14:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.59,1:14:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone discovers you,\Nthere will be such a terrible uproar!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.40,1:14:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.17,1:14:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose this breach of etiquette\Nis unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.70,1:14:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.44,1:14:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've longed to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.78,1:14:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,From the moment you left,\NI've been so afraid...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.92,1:14:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day, I dreaded getting word\Nabout you from the battlefield...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.55,1:15:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I prayed so hard for your well-being.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.23,1:15:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,God has answered my prayers.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.74,1:15:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.40,1:15:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so overcome with relief\Nthat I can't help my tears...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.78,1:15:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.01,1:15:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.63,1:16:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... There is nothing\Nto be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.10,1:16:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All the frightening things...\NAll the sad things...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.50,1:16:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just cast them into the fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.44,1:17:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pouring.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.21,1:17:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Griffith?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.08,1:17:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I haven't seen him since then.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.75,1:17:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.11,1:18:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take care...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.00,1:20:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well... If it isn't His Lordship,\Nthe future White Phoenix General.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.64,1:20:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you here\Nat this early hour?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.85,1:20:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You do realize whose palace this is?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.28,1:20:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There may even be cause\Nto charge you
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.02,1:20:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,with treason against\Nthe Midland's Royal House.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.02,1:20:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him away!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.60,1:20:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with Griffith?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.17,1:20:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Making us assemble like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.47,1:20:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably a surprise drill.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.08,1:20:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But we were told not\Nto bring any weapons.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.98,1:20:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably just a jaunt.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.58,1:21:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we beat Chuder,\Nwe haven't been in a decent battle.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.12,1:21:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But of all days...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.26,1:21:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't return at all yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.06,1:21:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It must've been\Na shock to Griffith, after all.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.13,1:21:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid! Something like that\Nwouldn't bother Griffith.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.03,1:21:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.80,1:21:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.50,1:21:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares if we lose a fool like him?!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.40,1:21:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith is a hero\Nwho rescued a nation!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.17,1:21:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He has no time to bother\Nwith one subordinate!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.41,1:21:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.18,1:21:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.01,1:21:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"But...but!" Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.71,1:21:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You just keep your mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.42,1:21:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since that guy left,\Neveryone's been so depressed!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.72,1:21:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of it!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.22,1:21:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, Griffith is late.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.99,1:21:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're being attacked!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.75,1:22:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this an ambush?!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.92,1:22:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.98,1:22:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Remnants from Chuder?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.32,1:22:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, hold on...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.65,1:22:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They're...!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.76,1:22:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Midland Army!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.80,1:22:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have known.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.57,1:22:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Common birth is something\Nyou cannot change.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.21,1:22:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,After I favored you,\Nthis is how you pay me back?!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.65,1:22:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over for you and your comrades!\NIt's all over!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.42,1:22:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I thought it was strange.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.66,1:22:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Political marriages are\Ncommon during wartime.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.16,1:22:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was never talk about\NPrincess Charlotte getting married.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.97,1:23:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying...?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.91,1:23:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to have Charlotte\Nfor yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.84,1:23:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.81,1:23:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You want her\Nto have you, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.59,1:23:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.49,1:23:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, we can't die until we find out\Nwhat the hell is going on!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.06,1:23:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.63,1:23:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us... Griffith...!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.74,1:23:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stay together.\NThey're aiming for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.41,1:23:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Corkus!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.81,1:23:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scatter!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.61,1:23:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way\Nwe'll break through them alone!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.65,1:23:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Get into formation!\NDon't give the enemy any chances!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.88,1:23:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll attack together\Nand make a run for it!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.12,1:23:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right!\N- Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.29,1:23:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, get into wedge formation!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.66,1:23:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.40,1:24:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.04,1:24:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Torturer!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.84,1:24:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.51,1:24:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you wish to this man.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.65,1:24:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He has sinned gravely\Nagainst Midland's Royal House.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.05,1:24:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're certain?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.96,1:24:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you must not kill him.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.56,1:24:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He shall be made to see the gravity\Nof his crime while he still breathes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.60,1:24:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.43,1:24:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The hawk has fallen to earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.64,1:24:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It will never take flight again.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.08,1:25:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You are something else.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.95,1:25:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been beaten to a pulp,\Nyet you haven't uttered a single cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.89,1:25:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm really impressed.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.02,1:25:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.03,1:25:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.06,1:25:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great! I want it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.40,1:25:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what a waste...\NI dropped it.

